window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She doesn't need anything but her bar....</b></p> <p>Daisy O'Dell has her hands full with hotheads and thirsty ranchers until the day one damn fine cowboy walks in and throws her whole life into turmoil....</p> <p><b>He's looking for a cold drink and a moment's peace....</b></p> <p>Instead, Jarod McElroy finds one red-hot woman. She's just what he needs - if only he can convince her to come out from behind that bar and come home with him....</p>"; 
